Privacy Policy
Last Updated: [19.08.2024]
Introduction
Welcome to MN-App Studio, a brand of Movie Network Pte. Ltd. (“we,” “our,” “us”). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data when you interact with our AI applications, including but not limited to AI Chat apps, Call Recorder apps, and other AI-powered applications we develop.
Information We Collect
We may collect various types of information to provide and improve our services, including:
Personal Information: Information that identifies you as an individual, such as your name, email address, or other contact information.
Usage Data: Information about how you use our apps, such as app interactions, preferences, and settings.
Device Information: Data related to your device, including but not limited to device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
To provide and maintain our applications and services.
To improve and enhance user experience.
To communicate with you regarding updates, promotions, or other relevant information.
To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights.
Data Security
We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
Third-Party Services
Our apps may use third-party services that collect information used to identify you. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of these third-party providers to understand their practices.
Your Rights
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights or have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at [insert contact email].
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.
